      "content": "it's just hard to see it that way when they look so much lighter when i'm not in the room. if i wasn't there constantly making mistakes or causing tension, they could actually have a normal, happy childhood. it feels like my presence is the thing holding them back from being okay. wouldn't it be better if they didn't have to carry my mess around anymore?",
